name: Color Smash
description:
Watch and play with 2D objects smash together, mixing colors whenever they do. Click any point to add a new shape with a random color. Controls ->

- press 't' to cycle through shapes
- press 's' to save image as png
- press 'r' to reset shapes
- press 'e' to erase image
- press 'p' to pause
- click any point to add a new shape

Enjoy
